
<section class="oe_container">
   <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
           <h2 class="oe_slogan">Sales Group - Multiple Sales Person on Sales Cycle</h2>
       <p class="oe_mt32">
This module allow you to have multiple sales person / group linked on CRM (Lead and Opportunity), Quotation/Sales Order, Invoice.<br/>
Using this module you can configure Sales Group where you are allowed to group multiple sales persons and which will form one group and linked to different documents.<br/>
Menu to Configure Sales Group: <b>Sales/Configuration/Sales Groups.</b>
       </p>
   </div>
</section>

